{"tid":454924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Pokémon Go團友臨終前拜託捉炎帝　台灣漢幫手圓願","createTime":"2017-11-01T15:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T04:53:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef8b0a7a10bec3195886dfc198bb3af2ed487b7","tid":454924,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171101/s00004/ae3f2d4bdfea5649da84ad5cdd0f2932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171101%2Fs00004%2Fae3f2d4bdfea5649da84ad5cdd0f2932.jpg&h=66d4b906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好的遊戲除了提供娛樂，亦會為玩家連結社會、認識朋友。手機遊戲Pok&eacute;mon Go就帶動玩家走出居所、聯黨結隊、認識新朋友，去年在香港引起一陣風潮。類似現象原來在台灣亦不例外，甚至有玩家即使絕症卧牀，仍想捕捉稀有的寵物，雖則這心願在他生前未能完成，但在死後還有團友幫手圓夢。<br />\n<br />\n台灣新北市的蔡章民網上發文，指由他管理的「林口寶可夢竹林群組」中，有位叫「老蕭」的朋友，在前日（10月30日）突然癌症復發，發燒送院。蔡章民指：「他住院期間一直掛念著要即將要出的炎帝」，和配以跟「老蕭」的對話截圖。圖中「老蕭」表示自己手腳麻木，無法拿手機，並表示：「想要拜託你捉頭目（炎帝），是要我手機給你還是帳號給你，還是有什麼需要。」<br />\n<br />\n蔡章民答應後就前去找「老蕭」，但到達後多次打電話給「老蕭」都沒有人接聽，後來是「老蕭」的兒子用其手機回覆蔡章民指：「我爸已經離開了。」蔡章民指，團友知道「老蕭」死了都十分難過，惟隨後又表示：「蕭大哥生前有個願望，我們想幫他達成。」<br />\n<br />\n蔡章民向「老蕭」兒子拿到其帳號，並和團友們在今日成功捉到「炎帝」，然後又把自己帳號的寵物改名為「老蕭的左右護法、坐騎及空軍部隊」，以示希望牠們護送「老蕭」到西方極樂。<br />\n<br />\n網友見文大表感動，蔡章民指這遊戲讓他瘦了5公斤，除了令他變得健康後，還可以獲得許多好友，藉著走出家門來聯繫感情。"},{"pid":"b033c8223d2d178e8728505787e237c427cd3131","tid":454924,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00004/1509543850800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00004%2F1509543850800&d=sGH9C0NDuTfP17pJWNnFV5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b1c24167\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00004%2F1509543850800&h=c9aeb229\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00004/1509543850800</a>"},{"pid":"84801bf88859888a94c2d0a2e4779a7fea2f9e30","tid":454924,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1d5c95240439cfcb405beab9d3188653d8c11f","tid":454924,"uid":8011,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"死左做來多鳩魚"},{"pid":"8565af216632c5a25f9cb6acaaf49eb996172c07","tid":454924,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"新北市+1"},{"pid":"4542f857035f7d1aa5443d6764283fd648221d1c","tid":454924,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"等睇男人既浪漫"},{"pid":"fe15d9e974b1b5e6f6708dd0e506b0d099a2beac","tid":454924,"uid":31652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"幾sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de71db8bb839f3109c2addd5cd86f7858a90d78f","tid":454924,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"臨死既願望係捉神獸...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係感動唔到喎大佬"},{"pid":"68a5715a7b81ef0e5e5a463cf180fb8aa818bbc3","tid":454924,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368cb1b7c13aef3704a580c93834ba5b7d1aa755","tid":454924,"uid":29093,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"到最尾你都堅持唔用外掛飛去外國炎帝 <br />\n最終由同伴幫你完成最後願望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絕對絕對值得尊敬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif